                        real-world action and earn rewards.
                    </p>
                    <img src="./images/Inspiration2.png" alt="inspiration" />
                </div>
                <!-- Overview Text and Image 3 -->
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl text-quietquest-dark">‚ú® Step 3: Earn Gold & Build Your Streak</h3>
                    <p class="font-afacad text-quietquest-dark">
                        Keep your streak alive by logging in daily. Defeating monsters grants gold, which you can use to unlock items,
                        upgrade your profile, and power up your quests.
                    </p>
                    <img src="./images/Inspiration3.png" alt="inspiration" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Div Container for Features Section -->
        <div class="bg-quietquest-gold py-24 mt-48 mb-48 px-6" id="features">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-16">
                <!-- Features Title -->
                <h2 class="font-combo text-quietquest-dark text-4xl">Features</h2>
                <!-- Features Text and Image 1 -->
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl text-quietquest-dark">üõ°Ô∏è Personalized Hero Paths</h3>
                    <p class="font-afacad text-quietquest-dark">
                        Choose your self-help focus‚Äîlike productivity, mindfulness, or energy‚Äîand get tasks and monsters tailored to your
                        path.
                    </p>
                    <img src="./images/Feature1.png" alt="Feature" />
                </div>
                <!-- Features Text and Image 2 -->
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl text-quietquest-dark">üë• Community Quests</h3>
                    <p class="font-afacad text-quietquest-dark">
                        Team up with friends or others on similar journeys. Join seasonal events to slay bigger monsters and unlock rare
                        items.
                    </p>
                    <img src="./images/Feature2.png" alt="Feature" />
                </div>
                <!-- Features Text and Image 3 -->
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl text-quietquest-dark">‚òÅÔ∏è Dynamic Weather Widget</h3>
                    <p class="font-afacad text-quietquest-dark">
                        Stay mindful of your environment with our real-time weather widget. This feature adapts to your location, displaying
                        current conditions and offering gentle suggestions‚Äîlike cozy tasks for rainy days or movement goals for sunny
                        afternoons.
                    </p>
                    <%- include('partials/weatherWidget') %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

